A program that gives you your chances of going home a winner or going home bankrupt when you play the American Roulette game at the Casino. This program assumes that you are utilizing the Martingale or “double your bet” strategy.

Inputs: 
	startingBet = The starting bet or bet increment you plan to go with based on the
	amountToSpend = amount you’re winning to spend.
	amountDesired = The goal amount that you wish to leave the casino with before you stop playing

Outputs: Your odds of winning or losing all your money
	